{"tid":22632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霸佔康樂場地! 點解工展會係維園舉辦?","createTime":"2016-12-04T14:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T17:32:32.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4fd6de102e68e32741b6124243d5e6e115aada","tid":22632,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"點解可以霸咗維園 6個足球場同埋籃球場攪工展會, 重要接近成個月時間. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(今年由 2016/12/10 - 2017/1/2, 計埋 set 場清場足一個月)<br />\n<br />\n維園足球場籃球場本身係康樂場地, 比市民免費使用.<br />\n工展會係一個純商業活動, 仲要收入場費 $10. <br />\n<br />\n相對, 花展要收入場費, 但都算文化康樂嘢.<br />\n年宵, 雖然係賣野, 但係傳統節慶, 而且免費入場<br />\n<br />\n點解要剝削市民既康樂活動設施, 去比商家攪工展會商業活動.<br />\n要攪商業活動, 咪去會展攪. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202f71a034b289164cde14ae8c7ece81243e709c","tid":22632,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"工展會租咁耐 要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb6dcf59d26b708d472d98e954d66ca08ec643c","tid":22632,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"冇一幅市區大型露天用地，可以大過維園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交通方便亦係其中因素 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c926d79e6d8d5bae5374629a5716e07b8e099ab4","tid":22632,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇一幅市區大型露天用地，可以大過維園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交通方便亦係其中因素 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工展會點解要露天? 日曬雨淋買野方便 D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交通方便, 會展唔方便??"},{"pid":"86786aa0590974252c31faa52e2887bfaace41de","tid":22632,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"歷史原因"},{"pid":"4